# Example configurations for popular services:
# ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Gmail:
#   SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
#   SMTP_PORT=587
#   SMTP_SECURE=tls
#   SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
#   SMTP_PASS=your-app-specific-password (from Google Account)
#
# SendGrid:
#   SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
#   SMTP_PORT=587
#   SMTP_SECURE=tls
#   SMTP_USER=apikey
#   SMTP_PASS=SG.xxxxxxxxxxxxx (your SendGrid API key)
#
# AWS SES:
#   SMTP_HOST=email-smtp.us-east-1.amazonaws.com (your region)
#   SMTP_PORT=587
#   SMTP_SECURE=tls
#   SMTP_USER=your-ses-user
#   SMTP_PASS=your-ses-password
#
